---Info  dr_sk_India-----

max players 50
48 CT
and 2 T
small map or medium size, but still hard.
1 secret.
9 Button's.

---Traps---
Trap 1.     One Routing wall, you can pass if you fast.
Trap 2.     Laser.  (No Button)
Trap 3.     Lightning strike.
Trap 4.     2 Walls come down and some black spears come out the wall.
Trap 5.     Jump over the quicksand + The terrorist can press a button.
Trap 6.     Jump to small blocks, if you fall you will die + one of the blocks will go down.
Trap 7.     Traps from the wall (left side).
Trap 8.     A Laser canon.
Trap 9.     Spikes in the air, and a block will push you up.
Trap 10.   A routing blade from the wall.
-----------------------
made by marnai.
